Watchlist

Where to Watch

This raunchy teen comedy blockbuster from producer Judd Apatow ("Knocked Up") centers on a trio of nerdy high-school friends who have a wild night of misadventures while trying to buy booze for a big graduation party. Jonah Hill, Michael Cera and Christopher Mintz-Plasse star. Directed by Greg Mottola.
